column2: First day in June that was both sunny and calm.  No rain.  No Powell Marsh water.
Sunny- calm.  Powell Marsh ditches loaded with iron floc.
Sunny- calm.  Little rain all summer (less than 1/2").  No water coming in from Powell Marsh.
Sunny- hot.  2 loons on lake.  No rain.  No water from Powell Marsh.
Breezy- sunny.  No water coming in from Powell Marsh.
Sunny.  Loons and gulls on lake.  No water coming in from Powell Marsh.
Sunny.  Light wind.  2" rain 2 days ago.  Small amount of water coming in from Powell Marsh.
Sunny- no wind at all.  Perfect for testing.
Sunny- 5 swans- ducks- loons- seagulls on lake.
